{"tid":357026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港7-Eleven接受「微信支付」　中國旅客可用人民幣消費","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T10:27:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8340cc8ff1def084cc5f98f2d6a7fd0ca6d76a95","tid":357026,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"中國流行利用電子貨幣消費，現時本港不少連鎖品牌亦接受中國旅客使用支付平台「微信支付」付費。「微信支付」現更進駐全港7-Eleven便利店，中國旅客可直接使用人民幣消費。<br />\n<br />\n本港便利店7-Eleven在昨日（11日）起與「微信支付」合作，內地旅客在全港900多家分店，可使用「微信支付」使用人民幣消費，系統會自動把人民幣兌換成港幣。<br />\n<br />\n「微信支付」更聯同香港7-Eleven推出優惠，包括由即日起至9月5日，在便利店使用「微信支付」消費滿30元人民幣，可減免10元人民幣。「微信支付」團隊表示，會投放更多資源在香港的跨境業務，協助香港商家為訪港內地旅客提供更好的服務。<br />\n<br />\n除了7-Eleven外，中國遊客在多個大型連鎖品牌亦可使用「微信支付」消費，包括海洋公園、六福珠寶、莎莎等。"},{"pid":"ce97b3fbec0c209725bd98b43e9969839ea3d5c2","tid":357026,"uid":135986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"快啲嘟完唔好阻住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fbb1b1b6d51fe552792dab10b40524022be80b","tid":357026,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170812/s00001/1502537776352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170812%2Fs00001%2F1502537776352&d=DcPKwM4bdEByzsU2II6dPpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=8de4d75d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170812%2Fs00001%2F1502537776352&h=6364b328\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170812/s00001/1502537776352</a>"},{"pid":"afc2cdf65863e71c9110b75a5efc98c14c6cdccb","tid":357026,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"7-11都投共"},{"pid":"bf09b5df760a890496aff06415ff5f6c9f77aa04","tid":357026,"uid":40397,"like":0,"disl